metadata.name: NFT.NYC 2023 General Admission Pass 1/750
metadata.description:
NFT.NYC, the leading annual Non-Fungible Token event returns to New York City in 2023 (April 12-14).

Each General Admission Pass is redeemable for a General Admission Ticket to the April 2023 event PLUS:

- 1 x bonus piece of merch from OpenSea and other NFT.NYC partners.
- The first 50 General Admission Passes minted will receive an additional General Admission Ticket at no charge.
- Mints 51-750 have a 1-in-5 chance of receiving a free upgrade from a General Admission Ticket to a VIP Access Ticket.

NFT.NYC 2023 Passes are modeled off the classic NFT.NYC official event pin, and are being made available exclusively on OpenSea. OpenSea has participated in NFT.NYC as its Foundational Partner since inception in 2018.

The holder of this NFT.NYC General Admission Pass can now redeem their benefits via https://app.nft.nyc/token/0x624B259F98D7Cb32a798320799AE0AEe73Ae7294/1
